{"id":576720,"title":"先睹为快：迷你CPU项目效果演示","content":"<p>你好，我是LMOS。</p><p>这个模块里，我们将一起设计一个迷你 RISCV 处理器。我准备了演示视频，让你先睹为快，看看我们最后做出的迷你CPU长什么样子。</p><p><video poster=\"https://media001.geekbang.org/eaa5b953a5b749f0b666bf35d7a99125/snapshots/cf7df2af8ec346ada2921ccf880dcfbe-00005.jpg\" preload=\"none\" controls=\"\"><source src=\"https://media001.geekbang.org/customerTrans/7e27d07d27d407ebcc195a0e78395f55/c951504-183875bde36-0000-0000-01d-dbacd.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"><source src=\" https://media001.geekbang.org/ead7dacfee594ac199e7834e6a45ea89/3ebc01acf76647b1bedcfded87b76f4f-39ba89e5e572464eeb280b658f4e0d5d-sd.m3u8\" type=\"application/x-mpegURL\"></video></p><p>看了视频，你有什么感受呢？先别急着动手敲代码，我们接下来会通过九节课的时间，从Verilog语言讲起，然后再进行迷你CPU的设计和实现。</p><p>希望通过这一阶段的学习，为你铺垫一些硬件的基础知识，也给你推开RISC-V的一扇窗。一起加油，希望在后面的留言区看到你的身影。</p><!-- [[[read_end]]] -->","neighbors":{"left":{"article_title":"02｜RISC特性与发展：RISC-V凭什么成为“半导体行业的Linux”？","id":541776},"right":{"article_title":"03｜硬件语言筑基（一）：从硬件语言开启手写CPU之旅","id":543867}},"comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":359188,"user_name":"😇","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":3068400,"ip_address":"湖北","ucode":"594695757BAD99","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/2e/d1/f0/0eafdb8e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1665309866,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"131070","content":"riscv32-unknown-elf-as -》riscv64-unknown-elf-as","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":"1345199","ctime":1666421996,"ip_address":"湖北","comment_id":359188,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5960277162","product_id":100117801,"comment_content":"老师你好，运行make asm后显示make[1]: riscv32-unknown-elf-as: 没有那个文件或目录<br>什么原因呢<br>","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1345199,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/86/af/99219321.jpg","nickname":"LMOS","note":"","ucode":"B037712C8B8B3C","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal